<br>
  Further, you seem to think that melees equipment really isn't necessary.  I would urge you to re- consider that stance.  Since it really makes no difference what equipment a tank has, i would assume you would be happy to go fight in PoJ with a warrior wearing crafted armor weilding a ssoy and a goranga club.  I mean, sure the warrior would never be able to maintain aggro, and when the mob eventaully ping- ponged onto him he would be eaten alive, but that's obviously beside the point, I mean, come on, all melee gear is really for is decoration.  Rusty short sword/ blade of carnage, wtf?!  Why do people even care so much, they're all the same.  Well, that's not exactly the conclusion I have drawn through my experience tanking, but hey, what would I really know?<br>
