  I have done my best to take an active role in this debate because it is on the GENERAL forum, and seems to be of great interest to a lot of people on this server, myself included.  However, Unnone, all you seem to be ableto do is release a volley of personal attacks and mean- spirited statements as opposed to making any genuine contibutions to this discussion.  There is a place for people who wish to act as you have, and it is on the flameboard.  Please do not act in this manner on a forum not intended for such actions.  And finally, if you have some problem with me as I relate to the guild i have chosen to seek membership in, Requiem, then please feel free to take your concerns up with an officer of that guild, a list of whom can be found at www.thehouseofrequiem.com.  Otherwise, as far as my status with any guild is concerned, I will ask you to politely mind your own business as such matters are wholly immaterial to this discussion.   <p>  Kazak- 57 Troll Warrior.<br>
